claim: Dumb and Dumber stars an award-winning actor.
premise_source_doc_sentence: 2012 festival award recipients included 2-time Academy-Award nominated actor Edward Norton , award-winning actor Matt Dillon , Academy-award winning actor Melissa Leo , Academy-award winning actor Octavia Spencer , multiple Emmy winning actor Allison Janney , actor Josh Lucas , and Academy-award nominated director Michael Apted .
